@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Listar todas as fotos
GET {{baseUrl}}/photos/

### Buscar foto por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/photos/1/

### Criar foto
POST {{baseUrl}}/photos/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "album": 1,
  "title": "Foto do pôr do sol",
  "url": "https://via.placeholder.com/600/92c952",
  "thumbnailUrl": "https://via.placeholder.com/150/92c952"
}

### Atualizar foto (completo)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/photos/1/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "album": 1,
  "title": "Título atualizado",
  "url": "https://via.placeholder.com/600/updated",
  "thumbnailUrl": "https://via.placeholder.com/150/updated"
}

### Atualizar foto (parcial)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/photos/1/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Só o título mudou"
}

### Deletar foto
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/photos/1/
